name: M.R.
text: I am being treated by Manali at Thrive Physio and Health. She is professional and knows her stuff.  We are lucky to have a physiotherapist who specializes in pelvic health for woman in our City.  Thrive has experienced physiotherapists  and can cover all aspects to help individuals achieve their health goals.
title: Thrive Physiotherapy and Wellness

name: B.O.
text: The experience was incredibly valuable and eye-opening. The doctor was exceptionally helpful, providing me with the assurance and confidence I needed for my upcoming labor and delivery. I was referred by my own doctor, and I can honestly say that it was well worth both the time and the investment.

text: Thrive physiotherapy is professional and caring. She is knowledgeable and explains everything in a way that you can understand the reasoning behind what she is doing. I noticed a reduction in pain after my first appointment. She prescribed stretches that you can log in to look at whenever you need. Excellent care and I recommend trying her!!
title: Thrive Physiotherapy and Wellness

name: S.B.
text: I am more than very happy nd satisfied with the quality of service  that I received at Thrive Physiotherapy , hence I decided to have Ms.Shanbhag as my family Physiotherapist :). Great location, easy parking and friendly front desk staff are the added benefits for the clients. I strongly recommend Thrive Physiotherapy for any one who would beneift from Physiotherapy service.
title: Thrive Physiotherapy and Wellness

name: N.G.
text: I've learned so many strategies to help with pain and strengthening during my pregnancy. Dr. Shanbhag has a gentle and holistic approach that helps to empower new and experienced mamas. I'm looking forward to continuing my therapy at Thrive postpartum!

name: C.R.
text: I was so nervous about my appointment but Manali was so great! Will definitely be going back and would highly recommend.

name: A.G.
text: A wonderful place. Manali is a wonderful and very knowledgeable physiotherapist, has a nice atmosphere, and does direct billing
title: Thrive Physiotherapy and Wellness

name: J.C.
text: Dr.Shanbhags compassion, and her approachable nature made it easy to discuss my concerns with her. She took her time understanding my issues and listening to me. I didn't find myself rushing to explain everything as a result I could clearly address my worries. She knew the appropriate treatment and excercises I needed. I started feeling improvement in one session. They also direct bill which is another plus. I highly recommend this place!!
title: Thrive Physiotherapy and Wellness

name: R.J.
text: Thrive physiotherapy is the first place I've ever been to for physiotherapy. I am amazed at the healing process due to laser therapy, and ultrasound procedures. Manali provides excellent service and advice. I would recommend their services.
title: Thrive Physiotherapy and Wellness

name: P.D.
text: Dr. Shanbhag provided quality care. The therapy and interventions addressed the area of concern and I was on the mend in just a few weeks.  I appreciated the fact that Manali researched my activities between appointments, so that she could address the problem. Overall, a very welcoming environment from the receptionist to my treatment with Manali.
title: Thrive Physiotherapy and Wellness
